      "date": "2025-05-01 23:01:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe following sessions will be run for build 113019 patch 1\n\nEnforced:\n- review-ldiskfs-dne on el8.10-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and clients\n- review-ldiskfs-dne on el9.4-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and clients\n- custom on el8.10-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and clients\n\nOptional:\n- review-ldiskfs-dne-arm on el8.10-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and el9.3-aarch64/ldiskfs clients\n\nMaloo Test Queue: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_queue?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=113019&commit=Apply+Filter\nMaloo Results: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/related?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=113019#redirect",
